title: How to Draw Nyan Cat

steps.headline: Draw a rectangle with rounded edges.
Draw a same shape inside of the 1st shape, but a little smaller.
Erase the middle area of the front part of the shape.
Draw a tail at the other end.
Make a rainbow coming out at the back area.
Add extra details to your image.
steps.description: Such details could include the stars and rest of space.

text: Draw a rectangle with rounded edges.  Draw a same shape inside of the 1st shape, but a little smaller.  Erase the middle area of the front part of the shape. Draw a cat head. Draw a tail at the other end.  Draw 2 paws at bottom right.  Draw 2 paws at bottom left.  Make a rainbow coming out at the back area.  Draw sprinkles in poptart.  Add extra details to your image. Such details could include the stars and rest of space. Color!
